---
// Visual block showing the paradox: writing becoming rarer but more valuable
---

<div class="reveal grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-0 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
  <!-- Left: writing becomes rarer -->
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-phase-discover to-phase-discover/80 p-8 md:p-10 text-white">
    <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] opacity-20 mb-4">&darr;</div>
    <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-3">Schrijven op papier wordt zeldzamer</h3>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-white/70 text-sm">
      <li>Op 96% van OESO-scholen hebben leerlingen digitale apparaten <sup class="text-white/40">1</sup></li>
      <li>Schrijfinstrumentenmarkt verschuift van volume naar waarde <sup class="text-white/40">2</sup></li>
      <li>Kantoor en onderwijs grotendeels gedigitaliseerd</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Right: writing becomes more valuable -->
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-phase-deliver to-phase-deliver/80 p-8 md:p-10 text-white">
    <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] opacity-20 mb-4">&uarr;</div>
    <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-3">Schrijven op papier wordt waardevoller</h3>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-white/70 text-sm">
      <li>Handschrift activeert hersengebieden die typen niet bereikt <sup class="text-white/40">3</sup></li>
      <li>Luxe schrijfwarensegment groeit met 4,6% per jaar <sup class="text-white/40">4</sup></li>
      <li>Zweden investeert $45 mln/jaar om handschrift terug te brengen <sup class="text-white/40">5</sup></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="text-xs text-dark/30 mt-3 space-y-0.5">
  <p>1. <a href="https://www.oecd.org/content/dam/oecd/en/publications/reports/2024/05/students-digital-devices-and-success_621829ff/9e4c0624-en.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-dark/50">OECD, PISA 2022 (2024)</a> &bull; 2. <a href="https://www.gminsights.com/industry-analysis/writing-instruments-market" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-dark/50">GM Insights (2025)</a> &bull; 3. <a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC10853352/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-dark/50">Van der Meer & Van der Weel, Frontiers in Psychology (2024)</a></p>
  <p>4. <a href="https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/01/23/3224629/0/en/Luxury-Writing-Instruments-and-Stationery-Market-Analysis-Report-2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-dark/50">GlobeNewsWire, Luxury Writing Instruments Market (2026)</a> &bull; 5. <a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2023/09/10/sweden-digital-education-backlash-reading-writing/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-dark/50">Washington Post (2023)</a></p>
</div>
